# =============================================================================
# AstraForge IDE - Example Environment Configuration
# =============================================================================
# 
# ‚ö†Ô∏è IMPORTANT: This is an EXAMPLE file!
# 
# To use:
# 1. Copy this file to create your actual .env file:
#    cp example.env .env
# 
# 2. Replace ALL placeholder values with your ACTUAL API keys
#    ‚ùå NEVER use "your-key-here" or similar placeholders
#    ‚úÖ Use your real API keys from the providers
#
# 3. The .env file is already in .gitignore - NEVER commit it!
#
